description:
Here is a brief selection of console RPG video game soundtracks, in MP3 format.  Some of them are commercial releases, some of them are amateur game rips.  None of them I did myself.  The bit rates and the encoding quality varies from soundtrack to soundtrack.  The list is by no means exhaustive, but I had a hard time finding some of these soundtracks so I am offering them here to make it easier for everybody else.  

These are the games:  Faxanadu (NES), Crystalis (NES), Secret of Evermore (SNES), Legend of Legaia (PS1), Alundra (PS1), Ultima Underworld (PS1), Star Ocean - The Second Story (PS1), Thousand Arms (PS1), Lunar Silver Star Story Complete (PS1), Threads of Fate (PS1), Lunar 2 Eternal Blue (PS1), Valkyrie Profile (PS1), Vandal Hearts (PS1); Chrono Trigger (SNES), Radical Dreamers (SV), Chrono Cross (PS1); Dragon Quest 1 &amp; 2 (SNES), Dragon Quest 3 (SNES), Dragon Quest 4 (NES), Dragon Quest 5 (SNES), Dragon Quest 6 (SNES), Dragon Quest 7 (PS1), Dragon Quest 8 (PS2); Seiken Densetsu (Gameboy), Secret of Mana (SNES), Seiken Densetsu 3 (SNES), Legend of Mana (PS1), Sword of Mana (GBA); plus a few remake soundtracks and covers.  I deliberately left out Final Fantasy, because those are pretty easy to find, and anyway I was always more into Dragon Warrior *pbbbbbt*!  (I reaaaally hate anime cut-scenes!)  :)

